                you a new local number. You choose. The redirect is done with a
                simple code we send, without changing carrier.
              </div>
            </details>
            <details class="faq">
              <summary>
                <span class="faq-arrow">‚ñ∂</span>
                Can I listen to the recordings?
              </summary>
