                <ul class="faq-list">
                  <li>View transcripts and recordings of each call</li>
                  <li>Upload and update your knowledge base (property catalog)</li>
                  <li>Run outbound calls to contact lists</li>
                  <li>Check stats (cities, schedules, conversion rate)</li>
                  <li>Adjust Laura's tone and behavior</li>
                </ul>
                Everything updates in real time, no coding required.
              </div>
            </details>
            <details class="faq">
              <summary>
                <span class="faq-arrow">‚ñ∂</span>
                What languages can she speak?
              </summary>
              <div class="faq-content">
                Laura detects the customer's language and switches instantly.
                By default she works in Spanish and English. If you need more
                languages (French, German, Portuguese), we activate them at no
                extra cost from the dashboard.
              </div>
            </details>
            <details class="faq">
              <summary>
                <span class="faq-arrow">‚ñ∂</span>
                Can I try it without commitment?
              </summary>
              <div class="faq-content">
                Yes. Book a 15-minute demo where we show you the dashboard, do
                live test calls, and answer your questions. If you decide to
                activate it, you can cancel anytime with no contract.
              </div>
            </details>
            <details class="faq">
              <summary>
                <span class="faq-arrow">‚ñ∂</span>
                Do I have to install anything?
